                      Updated Tuesday, January 29, 2002

   Monthly Consumer Caseload Reports
          Number of consumers by regional center and status code.

   Developmental Disabilities: An Update for Health Professionals
          A 2-day Continuing Medical Education Course Presented by:
          University of California San Francisco of Medicine and
          University of California San Diego School of Medicine.

                        Previous Updates & Additions:

   Community Program Development Grants (Added 1/22/2002)
          The State Council on Developmental Disabilities seeks proposals
          for new programs that are creative, special, and innovative for
          people with developmental disabilities and their families.

   Governor's Budget (Added 1/10/2002)
          Highlights from the Fiscal Year 2002-2003 Governor's Budget for
          the Department of Developmental Services.

   New Appointment (Added 1/2/2002)
          DDS is pleased to announce the appointment of its new Chief
          Counsel to the Office of Legal Affairs, Catherine R. Ewing.

   State Capitol Tree Lighting Ceremony (Added 1/2/2002)
          Davis Wood of Mammoth Lakes, CA, participates with the State
          Capitol Tree Lighting Ceremony.

   DDS Fact Book - Fourth Edition (Added 1/2/2002)
          The DDS Fact Book offers a look at the demographics and
          characteristics of persons served by DDS.

   Title 17 Proposed Regulations (Added 12/21/2001)
          Special Incident Reporting

   Year 2 Direct Support Professional Training Resource Guide (Added
          12/19/2001)
          A curriculum manual for Direct Support Professionals.

   Crisis Intervention for Persons with Developmental Disabilities (Added
          12/4/2001)
          A Report to the Legislature.

   Spanish Language Version of Regional Center Video (Added 9/13/2001)
          This video shares the real stories of families and the role
          regional centers play in the State of California.

   A Consumer's Guide to the Lanterman Act (Added 8/16/2001)
          A 52-page booklet for adults with developmental disabilities
          written with the help of consumers.

   Supported Living Services (Added 6/20/2001)
          Updated Supported Living Services home page along with new
          links.

   Strategic Plan 2001-2006 (Added 5/8/2001)
          The Strategic Plan 2001-2006 provides a high-level overview of
          the desired future and goals for DDS.
